Currently some parts of the North West province and Northern Cape are experience high temperatures. JOHANNESBURG The South African Weather Service has issued a warning of a possible heatwave in Gauteng next week. Currently some parts of the North West province and Northern Cape are experience high temperatures.Forecaster Wayne Venter says Gauteng residents should brace themselves for extremely high temperatures. We are seeing there possibility of a heatwave in Gauteng, from Tuesday or Wednesday. (Edited by Masechaba Sefularo)